item.title: More Resources To Reference
item.description: List Of Books You cannot read all books containing valuable information in a thousand lifetimes. The trick is knowing which ones to read. This list has the possibility of being modified over time. 12 Rules for Life: An Antidote to Chaos - Jordan Peterson Maps of Meaning: The Architecture of Belief - Jordan Peterson 48 Laws of Power - Robert Greene The Unplugged Alpha - Richard Cooper
